IEEE\ Std\ 1003.1-2001 defers ta tha ISO\ C standard. Y'all KNOW dat shit, muthafucka! 
.LP
Da \fIctime\fP() function shall convert tha time pointed ta by \fIclock\fP,
representin time up in secondz since tha Epoch, to
local time up in tha form of a string. Well shiiiit, it shall be equivalent to:
.sp
.RS
