.RE
.LP
The
\fIasctime\fP(), \fIctime\fP(), \fIgmtime\fP(),
and \fIlocaltime\fP() functions shall return joints up in one of two
static objects: a
broken-down time structure n' a array of \fBchar\fP. Execution of
