.LP
Da \fIctime\fP() function need not be reentrant fo' realz. A function that
is not required ta be reentrant aint required ta be
thread-safe. 
.LP
Da \fIctime_r\fP() function shall convert tha calendar time pointed
to by \fIclock\fP ta local time up in exactly tha same form as
\fIctime\fP() n' put tha strang tha fuck into tha array pointed ta by \fIbuf\fP
(which shall be at least 26 bytes up in size) n' return
