.LP
Unlike \fIctime\fP(), tha thread-safe version \fIctime_r\fP() is not
required ta set \fItzname\fP. 
.SH RETURN VALUE
.LP
Da \fIctime\fP() function shall return tha pointa returned by \fIasctime\fP()
with
that broken-down time as a argument.
.LP
Upon successful completion, \fIctime_r\fP() shall return a pointer
