\fIlocaltime\fP(). Da \fIctime\fP() function is included fo' compatibility
with older
implementations, n' do not support localized date n' time formats.
Applications should use tha \fIstrftime\fP() function ta big up maximum
portability.
.LP
Da \fIctime_r\fP() function is thread-safe n' shall return joints
